text: Thesh, or Tjesh, Tesh etc., was a Predynastic ancient Egyptian king who ruled in the Nile Delta.J. H. Breasted, History of Egypt from the Earliest Time to the Persian Conquest, 1909, p.36 He is mentioned in the Palermo Stone inscriptions among a small number of kings of Lower Egypt J. H.
